{"tid":1799421,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"朋友想搞個youtube channel幫抗爭基金","createTime":"2019-12-27T02:58:14.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-27T04:18:39.000Z","uid":24284,"like":2,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"2e8bf5844ba566471017260552ccd56263fe0d7e","tid":1799421,"uid":24284,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-27T02:58:14.000Z","msg":"陸續有好多手足嘅官司，加上appeal，會洗好多錢，所以朋友想搞個Channel賺錢俾抗爭基金。<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/cheerup.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nChannel所有收入最少有95%-99%會捐俾612/星火/其他(eg.保護傘計畫)，而其他1-5%會用作日常開支。<br />\n<br />\n因為暫時為試驗階段，未有營利，當有營利將會開放監察(eg. 議員)。<br />\n另外因為業餘製作，無剪片無盛，質素好參差<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/itdog3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，有共同諗法嘅朋友可以透過呢度搵我朋友。<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n大家俾啲意見<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />: <a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=3zrGEhIwL2I\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3D3zrGEhIwL2I&d=TEMpI0ru4fZij%2BnpPgfFHcjT01h1KCp2%2Bw2KB0oDRGE%3D&h=24532c7a\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=3zrGEhIwL2I</a>"},{"pid":"e2a9df3d12a4b5dc1dfe617d6ae6be293186021c","tid":1799421,"uid":24284,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-27T03:00:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/itdog1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b5eefad975d5c36e5a54f114e8bb24b325c87398","tid":1799421,"uid":219445,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-27T03:01:01.000Z","msg":"你朋友想搞點解你朋友唔上黎講?"},{"pid":"f8f349ba83ac143d6054d57574c66556f4173d83","tid":1799421,"uid":37054,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-27T03:01:09.000Z","msg":"學開掛之達人賺完錢就消失?"},{"pid":"08dd90be88eb5667dfcdafbf6b2e053a3a79ed9b","tid":1799421,"uid":24284,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"f8f349ba83ac143d6054d57574c66556f4173d83","tid":1799421,"uid":37054,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"reply